### STEP 07: Build Financial Controls

**Script**: `2.7_BuildFinancialControls.py`

**Inputs**:
- `4_Outputs/2.5c_FilterCallsAndCeos/latest/f1d_enriched_ceo_filtered_YYYY.parquet` (17 files)
- `1_Inputs/tr_ibes/tr_ibes.parquet` (I/B/E/S earnings surprise data)
