6. Winsorize EPS growth at [1%, 99%]
7. Create surprise decile bins
8. Save call-level data with all controls

**Outputs**:
- `4_Outputs/2.7_BuildFinancialControls/{timestamp}/calls_with_controls_YYYY.parquet`
  - All columns from Step 2.5c plus:
